pageContext.claim: “So in California, the Democrats, who fought like crazy to get all mail in only ballots, and succeeded, have just opened a voting booth in the most Democrat area in the State. They are trying to steal another election. It’s all rigged out there. These votes must not count. SCAM!”
pageContext.analysis: How in the world is it rigging an election to open an in-person polling location? Trump makes no effort to explain.
